    <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
        <h1>EXPERIMENTATION</h1>
        <p class="project-description">The business decided to build the product in-house. Three large districts were selected to test feature during the next enrollment cycle. Special instructions and regulations were given to these districts to measure success rates of automated secure FTP.</p>
